## Future Work

- Incorporate wrist sensor signals (BVP, ACC) for higher accuracy
- Explore transformer-based architectures for sequence modeling
- Build a real-time inference pipeline from live wearable data
- Extend to continuous affect monitoring beyond discrete labels

